finely grated fresh lemon zest	2	teaspoons	
fresh lemon juice	1/2	cup	
strawberries	1	pound	
confectioners' sugar	1/2	cup	
salt	1/4	teaspoon	
sugar	1 1/2	cups	
unsalted pistachios (preferably not roasted)	3	tablespoons	
heavy cream	1	cup	
large egg whites	4		
large eggs	3		
unsalted butter	3/4	stick	
special equipment: 2 large baking sheets; parchment paper; a stand mixer or a powerful handheld electric mixer; a pastry bag fitted with a plain, round 1/2-inch tip (we used wilton 1a)			
